Brief review: Metric anomalies, trace spikes and log row_count drops consistently point to cartservice-0 as the downstream faulty pod. Trace and log anomalies first appear at 2022-03-20 15:08:00 (Asia/Shanghai, UTC+8). Node-6 (where cartservice-0 runs) showed elevated TCP retransmits earlier in the window, and cartservice-0's container network/mesh metrics, memory/IO and trace durations spiked at 15:08, consistent with network retransmission/packet loss causing request retries and traffic disappearance.

```json
